     H            Y.
     F** UTLR62D***********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY- GET CUSTOMER GROUP & GROUP NAME    *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)                                    *
     F*           2026.03.11                                  *
     F*-------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR62D'
     F*                    PARM           $DLV    4
     F*                    PARM           $GRP    3
     F*                    PARM           $GNAM  10
     F*  IN  $DLV  :  4A DELIVERY#
     F*  OUT $GRP  :  3A GROUP CODE
     F*      $GNAM : 10A GROUP NAME
     F******************************************************
     FEDIPP43 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
      * GET GROUP CODE
     C                     CALL 'UTLR62B'
     C                     PARM           $DLV    4
     C                     PARM           $GRP    3
     C                     PARM           $NAME1 15
     C                     PARM           $NAME2 50
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
      * GET GROUP NAME
     C           $GRP      CHAINEDIPP43              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELE3GPNM    $GNAM
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $GNAM
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *======================================================
      * INITIAL SET
      *======================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $DLV    4
     C                     PARM           $GRP    3
     C                     PARM           $GNAM  10
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $GRP
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $GNAM
      *
     C                     ENDSR
